getServices

public Set<String> getServices()
Get the immutable set of services to place on a cluster by default. When solving for a cluster layout, a set of services can be given to the solver to place on the cluster. If no service set is given, this default set will be used.

Returns:
Immutable set of services that will be placed on the cluster by default.
